078    public static <T extends ApiMethod<T, TResult> & ExpandableTrait<T>, TResult, TQuery extends MetaModelGetDsl<?, ?, ?, ?>> T get(
079            final T request, final TQuery getDsl) {
080        T updatedRequest = request;
081        for (ExpansionPath<?> expansionPath : getDsl.expansionPaths()) {
082            updatedRequest = (T) updatedRequest.addExpand(expansionPath.toSphereExpand());
083        }
084        return updatedRequest;
085    }
086
087    public static <T extends ApiMethod<T, TResult> & ExpandableTrait<T>, TResult, TQuery extends MetaModelGetDsl<?, ?, ?, ?>> T get(
088            final T request, final Supplier<TQuery> createGetDsl, final Function<TQuery, TQuery> getDsl) {
089        MetaModelGetDsl<?, ?, ?, ?> get = getDsl.apply(createGetDsl.get());
090        return get(request, get);
091    }
092
093    public <T extends ApiMethod<T, TResult> & ExpandableTrait<T>, TResult, TQuery extends MetaModelGetDsl<?, ?, ?, ?>> T with(
094            final Function<ProjectApiRoot, T> request, final Supplier<TQuery> createGetDsl,
095            final Function<TQuery, TQuery> getDsl) {
096        MetaModelGetDsl<?, ?, ?, ?> get = getDsl.apply(createGetDsl.get());
097        return get(request.apply(apiRoot), get);
098    }
